 ARGS ANIMATE DIR;JD1;JD2;NDAYS;I;PAD;FN;START;END;T;LA;LO
вЌќ Generate SVG frames for animation, one per day
вЌќ ARGS: (M D Y)(M D Y) TIME LAT LONG вЂ” start date, end date, UTC time, lat, long
вЌќ DIR: output directory (must exist)
вЌќ Writes frame_00001.svg through frame_NNNNN.svg
 START END T LA LOв†ђARGS
 JD1в†ђJNU START
 JD2в†ђJNU END
 NDAYSв†ђ1+JD2-JD1
 :For I :In вЌіNDAYS
   STATEDDAYNOв†ђJD1+I-1
   STATEDTIMEв†ђT
   LATв†ђLA в‹„ LONGв†ђLO
   TIMEв†ђLO TIMEADJUST T
   DATEв†ђSTATEDDAYNO+(TIMEГ·24)-LOГ·360
   CALCULATEPLANETS
   CALCULATESTARS
   PADв†ђ'00000',вЌ•I
   FNв†ђDIR,'/frame_',(ВЇ5в†‘PAD),'.svg'
   (вЉ‚FRAMESVG)вЋ•NPUT FN 1
 :EndFor
 вЋ•в†ђ'Generated ',(вЌ•NDAYS),' frames in ',DIR
